  array('id' => '133','post_id' => '37','key' => 'excerpt','value' => 'WhatsML allows you to send text, media, and template messages in bulk, either instantly or on a schedule. You can launch promotional campaigns, reminders, or customer follow-ups using simple tools. Scheduled campaigns allow you to automate message delivery at specific times, while triggered campaigns can be set up based on user behavior or chatbot interactions.'),
  array('id' => '134','post_id' => '38','key' => 'excerpt','value' => 'Yes, WhatsML supports intelligent automation using OpenAI-powered chatbots. You can configure your bot to respond automatically using AI fine-tuned on your custom data or NLP datasets. The system allows you to create keyword-based auto replies, smart FAQ bots, or fully conversational flows that operate 24/7 without human intervention.'),
  array('id' => '135','post_id' => '39','key' => 'excerpt','value' => 'To get started, you can connect your WhatsApp number using either the Cloud API method or the Web API method. With the Cloud API, you just need to enter your API credentials and webhook URL. For the Web API, simply scan the QR code or enter the pairing code provided. Once the device is successfully linked, the system will mark it as "Ready", and you can begin sending messages.'),
  array('id' => '136','post_id' => '40','key' => 'excerpt','value' => 'WhatsML is an AI-driven WhatsApp marketing and automation platform that helps businesses engage their audience more effectively. It combines both WhatsApp Cloud API and WhatsApp Web API, allowing users to send bulk messages, run campaigns, set up AI chatbots, manage real-time conversations, and analyze campaign performance—all from a single dashboard.'),
  array('id' => '143','post_id' => '43','key' => 'excerpt','value' => 'WhatsML has completely transformed how we handle client communication. The AI auto-replies are super accurate, and the campaign automation saved us hours every week.'),
